description: During the " Iran-Venezuela Cultural Relations" meeting held on Monday, March 11, at the Bolivarian University of Venezuela, Meta's action in removing the pro-Palestinian pages of Imam Khamenei from Instagram and Facebook was condemned in the presence of a number of intellectuals and university professors.
title: Meta closing Leader's social media pages proof falseness of freedom of expression

description: TEHRAN – Mohammad Kazemian was elected as president of Iran Equestrian Federation on Thursday for a four-year term till 2028.
title: Kazemian elected president of Iran Equestrian Federation
